                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8800" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0259</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1713 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">形似？神至！——头雁引领的长春供热集团公司治理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Likeness? Divine!—The road of governance of Changchun Heating Group Company led by leading geese</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王旭，罗镇涛，许瀚文，曹雨潭</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长春市供热（集团）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司治理机制；国有企业；党组织；董事长；权责配置；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate governance mechanism; State-owned enterprises; Party organization; Chairman of the board; Allocation of authority and responsibil</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业建立健全权责明晰、权责透明、协调运转、有效制衡的公司治理机制是完善中国特色国有企业现代公司治理的内在要求。本案例讲述了长春供热集团完善公司治理结构、优化公司治理机制的过程，聚焦于国有独资企业治理主体权责划分、外部董事作用发挥等问题，重点探讨董事长在国有独资企业公司治理当中如何发挥作用，推动中国特色的现代公司治理效能充分实现。长春供热集团在董事长——“头雁”的带领下，不断增强党委“把方向、管大局、保落实”的领导作用，更好地发挥董事会“定战略、作决策、防风险”的作用，进一步保障经理层“谋经营、抓落实、强管理”的职责。通过对本案例的分析，有助于学生学习国有企业公司治理结构和运行机制，辨析国有企业公司治理的重要问题，思考如何优化国有企业公司治理机制，形成合理的权责配置，推动国有企业运行效率的提升。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Establishing and improving the corporate governance mechanism of state-owned enterprises with clear rights and responsibilities, transparent rights and responsibilities, coordinated operation and effective checks and balances is the inherent requirement for improving the modern corporate governance of state-owned enterprises with Chinese characteristics. This case describes the process of improving the corporate governance structure and optimizing the corporate governance mechanism of Changchun Heating Group, focusing on issues such as the division of rights and responsibilities of the governance body of the wholly state-owned enterprise, the role of external directors, etc., focusing on how the chairman plays his role in the corporate governance of the wholly state-owned enterprise, and promoting the full realization of modern corporate governance effectiveness with Chinese characteristics. Through the analysis of this case, it is helpful for students to learn the corporate governance structure and operation mechanism of state-owned enterprises, identify important issues of corporate governance of state-owned enterprises, think about how to optimize the corporate governance mechanism of state-owned enterprises, form a reasonable allocation of rights and responsibilities, and promote the improvement of the operation efficiency of state-owned enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司治理结构；公司治理运作机制；国有企业概念及类型；党组织与公司治理；分层授权理论；高层梯队理论；公司治理文化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
